{"tid":994438,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"微軟搜尋器Bing傳內地遭屏蔽","createTime":"2019-01-24T16:44:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T19:23:10.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c8fde38a77ad418192889fc7f871ee148f1c1ebf","tid":994438,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T16:44:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2019/01/24/2045737_6b8a0eee72079da6c09c5a3fe28d1ef7_320.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2019%2F01%2F24%2F2045737_6b8a0eee72079da6c09c5a3fe28d1ef7_320.jpg&h=527aa0a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n微軟(Microsoft)旗下Bing搜尋器據報於中國遭屏蔽。<br />\n<br />\n英國《金融時報》引述消息人士報道，在中國政府的命令下，微軟的Bing搜尋器已在中國被屏蔽。<br />\n<br />\n有內地用戶在社交媒體上發文指出，<a href=\"http://無法訪問Bing的中國網站cn.bing.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E7%84%A1%E6%B3%95%E8%A8%AA%E5%95%8FBing%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99cn.bing.com&d=hdqsaZ39PhFSvpGPh6wjSrDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=5669e17c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">無法訪問Bing的中國網站cn.bing.com</a>；在中國境外，該網站仍可訪問。微軟表示，正在調查這情況。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述了解中國政府命令的消息人士證實，Bing已遭屏蔽，又指中國國有電訊公司之一的中國聯通證實，政府已下令屏蔽Bing。<br />\n<br />\n在2010年谷歌(Google)的搜尋器擎退出中國市場後，Bing成為中國境內僅剩的一家知名外國搜尋器，此次屏蔽將它也移出了中國市場。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2045737/%E5%BE%AE%E8%BB%9F%E6%90%9C%E5%B0%8B%E5%99%A8Bing%E5%82%B3%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E9%81%AD%E5%B1%8F%E8%94%BD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F2045737%2F%25E5%25BE%25AE%25E8%25BB%259F%25E6%2590%259C%25E5%25B0%258B%25E5%2599%25A8Bing%25E5%2582%25B3%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%25B1%258F%25E8%2594%25BD&d=hdqsaZ39PhFSvpGPh6wjSrDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=15aeedc9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/2045737/%E5%BE%AE%E8%BB%9F%E6%90%9C%E5%B0%8B%E5%99%A8Bing%E5%82%B3%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E9%81%AD%E5%B1%8F%E8%94%BD</a>"},{"pid":"5e79a4acfefb7159e609dafa1f2ff823aebd0e24","tid":994438,"uid":24788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T16:53:30.000Z","msg":"冰"},{"pid":"165e356f327ca2984c181088bf3bd45be2ad9e64","tid":994438,"uid":9838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T17:00:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9fa463b5113b869d621b83b8f695457bc68047e","tid":994438,"uid":37666,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T18:56:21.000Z","msg":"Bing<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家仲有冇人用?"},{"pid":"55f6f95ce88e461bfed09530effbaea51881aac1","tid":994438,"uid":50124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9fa463b5113b869d621b83b8f695457bc68047e","tid":994438,"uid":37666,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T18:56:21.000Z","msg":"Bing<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家仲有冇人用?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T19:14:39.000Z","msg":"美國多，其他多數國家都google佔9成"},{"pid":"a4625e72f7f92044fb5e56b60c4fa57acdddf81b","tid":994438,"uid":59737,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T19:23:10.000Z","msg":"奶共最後都係要收皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}